The paper discusses a deep learning model for extractive Question Answering (QA) and proposes a system that uses pre-training and fine-tuning on labeled examples. These topics are commonly discussed in the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Computer Vision (cs.CV).
